## Purpose
This document outlines the governance framework implemented in the 
ServiceNow CMDB Governance Lab.

## CI Classes Used
- Business Service (cmdb_ci_service)
- Application (cmdb_ci_appl)
- Server (cmdb_ci_server)
- Database (cmdb_ci_db_instance)

## Relationship Types
- Depends on::Used by — service dependency
- Runs on::Runs for — application to server
- Connects to::Connected by — server to database

## Data Quality Controls
- Business Rule: blocks CI saves without owner assigned
- Import Set coalesce: prevents duplicate CI creation on re-import

## Audit Readiness
- All CIs have assigned owners
- Dependency chain is fully documented
- CMDB health reports provide continuous visibility
